    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I know that this is a comment on an old recipe, but I wanted you to know that I stirred polenta in with the kale and broth while it was cooking and stirred every few minutes.  It is a riff on a Bittman recipe from a couple of years ago.  Anyways, polenta, kale and an olive oil fried egg on top &#8211; yum!  (Anything is better with an egg on top!)</p>
