    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I love Kale in my fave soup. Portugese kale soup. It&#39;s just a little olive oil in a stock pot. Then add 2 peeled &#038; chopped carrots, 1 chopped lg to med onion, &#038; turkey sausage sliced. Slowly saute&#39; 10 mins. Add 6 cps chicken broth &#038; 1 cup water &#038; bring to a boil. Add 1 bunch of torn or chopped kale withoy the stems &#038; simmer 20 min&#39;s. Delicious. I&#39;m trying your recipe tonight for supper. Thanks. Sounds great.</p>
    </div>

